Computer Message: Honourable Citizens, \nWe've received troublesome reports that our enemies have survived in an underground bunker not unlike ours. 
Computer Message: They're continuing their excavation efforts further down, as if to prepare for an even more dangerous bombing. 
Computer Message: It is clear that this is a ridiculous provocation aimed at escalating the conflict that has already destroyed Mother Earth.
Computer Message: Once again in these troubling times, we are reminded that freedom has a price. We cannot allow the mineshaft gap between our bunkers grow any longer. 
Computer Message: Starting now, most of our citizenry will be redirected to mine further down.
#Computer Message: President of the European Commision,\nMarch 2174
=> END